This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with building a dependency treebank for Vietnamese, which is a crucial resource for natural language processing. The paper also discusses experiments on POS tagging and dependency parsing, which are important tasks in computational linguistics. 

It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for POS tagging and dependency parsing. 

Additionally, it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper deals with developing a resource for natural language processing, which is a subfield of AI. 

It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the paper discusses the use of neural networks for POS tagging and dependency parsing. 

Finally, it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the paper deals with developing a resource that can be used for information retrieval tasks in Vietnamese.
